1
00:00:02,779 --> 00:00:04,200
You've got a good heart.

2
00:00:04,219 --> 00:00:05,900
Don't ever lose it.

3
00:00:05,960 --> 00:00:10,220
No matter how the world tries to break you, protect the family.

4
00:00:14,460 --> 00:00:17,760
My sister is gone.

5
00:00:19,019 --> 00:00:22,899
War is coming.

6
00:00:25,300 --> 00:00:27,800
We do not lament death.

7
00:00:27,859 --> 00:00:30,800
We avenge it.

8
00:00:40,219 --> 00:00:44,579
We can't change what fate has in store for us.

9
00:00:46,820 --> 00:00:48,859
But we don't have to face it alone.

10
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:51,119
Never a dull moment.

11
00:01:06,659 --> 00:01:08,959
The arcane is waking up.

12
00:01:10,719 --> 00:01:14,640
There's a monster inside all of us.

13
00:01:18,799 --> 00:01:20,519
It's time to let the monster out.

14
00:01:32,549 --> 00:01:33,900
We'll show them.

15
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:36,959
We will show them all.